msgctxt "talk15"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Gerudo Town is west of Hateno Village\n"
"way out in the <2.se_co>Gerudo Desert<3.re_co>.\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>Right when I was about to make my way\n"
"into Gerudo Town, the gatekeeper drove\n"
"me off...\n"
"<5.so>Wasn't until later that I heard they only\n"
"let women in there!\n"
"\n"
"<6.so>Now, had I known that beforehand, I\n"
"wouldn't have trekked all the way across\n"
"that stinking wasteland of a desert!\n"
"<7.so>But now I'm here wondering if I could've\n"
"actually gotten in there if I'd <8.se_co>fooled them\n"
"into thinking I belonged<9.re_co>..."
msgstr ""

