msgid ""
"<1.so>Other places?\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Well, if you've got a taste for adventure,\n"
"you don't want to miss out on\n"
"Zora's Domain and Rito Village.\n"
"The road to Zora's Domain is dangerous,\n"
"though. And Rito Village is way far away.\n"
"Neither are easy places to get to."
msgstr ""

